<br>
I remember being on lists for the first room in Dead side of guk (the bed room), can't even remember the name of the camp.  I never saw a Frenzy or LMH group, those were camped solid.<br>
<br>
Everyone was in my opinion more kind.  We actually payed attention to each other, there were nakid gnome races and archery contests.<br>
<br>
Tp's were pretty uncommon, compared to know anyways.  Runs from GFay to Erudin were a regular thing for me.  Boats were broken even then.<br>
<br>
So on and so on... this is just what I can remember.  I'm sure others can add their own touch to this thread.<br>
<br>
