<br>
I just asked people walking around how to get to freeport and it took me about 6 hours to get there.. (at that time i played a lvl 10 cleric). <br>
<br>
It was not easy to get a bind in freeport mostly because people above lvl 14 were rather rare.<br>
<br>
At one time there was a character complete in Bronze .. everyone went out to see him! he was really Uber that time! and pickup groups everywhere! unrest, befallen, almost all outdoor zones!.. <br>
<br>
Possesing a magical weapon before lvl 20 was really awesome but rare.. I had my Runed Totem Staff around lvl 15 (bought it for an enormous amount of 25PP!) that one lasted very long!<br>
<br>
I hunted in guk long times because we wanted to get a full set of really awesome monk armour for my monk friend! (mesh!).<br>
<br>
Anyway. . I had a lot of fun those days.. but I must say that I still have a lot of fun these days.. (mostly because of social contacts with guildmembers) and also because I really feel powerfull now with my mage (cleared the graveyard in mistmoore yesterday with my lvl 36 mage.. i don't think I could have done that in the early days or with another character!)<br>
